    "subject": "Physics",
    "topic": "wheatstone-bridge",
    "difficulty": "easy",
    "solution": "<p>Balanced wheatstone bridge.</p>\n<p>$$\\Rightarrow \\quad 12 \\times 0.5=(x+6) \\times \\frac{1}{2} \\Rightarrow x=6 \\Omega$$</p>",
    "section": "A",
