  {
    "id": "ldqw5clm",
    "questionNumber": 24,
    "questionText": "<p>If the potential difference between $\\mathrm{B}$ and $\\mathrm{D}$ is zero, the value of $x$ is $\\frac{1}{n} \\Omega$. The value of $n$ is __________.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/fly/@width/image/1ldr05kng/f041fd9d-3631-49b8-b2c2-9aa057889af3/326a90c0-a51e-11ed-8305-97c1292784a6/file-1ldr05knh.png?format=png\" data-orsrc=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/image/1ldr05kng/f041fd9d-3631-49b8-b2c2-9aa057889af3/326a90c0-a51e-11ed-8305-97c1292784a6/file-1ldr05knh.png\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"max-width:100%;height:auto;display:block;margin:0px auto;max-height:40vh\" alt=\"JEE Main 2023 (Online) 30th January Evening Shift Physics - Current Electricity Question 134 English\"></p>",
