    "negativeMarks": -1,
    "subject": "Physics",
    "topic": "wheatstone-bridge",
    "difficulty": "medium",
    "solution": "<p>The circuit is a Wheatstone bridge, so</p>\n<p>$${{{{6 \\times 3} \\over {6 + 3}}} \\over {{{x \\times 1} \\over {x + 1}}}} = {{1 + 2} \\over x}$$</p>\n<p>$$ \\Rightarrow {{2(x + 1)} \\over x} = {3 \\over x}$$</p>\n<p>$$ \\Rightarrow x = {1 \\over 2}$$</p>\n<p>So $$n = 2$$</p>",
    "section": "B",
    "type": "NUMERICAL"
