    "id": "1l6i19h3h",
    "questionNumber": 7,
    "questionText": "<p>A battery of $$6 \\mathrm{~V}$$ is connected to the circuit as shown below. The current I drawn from the battery is :</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/fly/@width/image/1l6kp6abb/cd2e5b45-a0bb-4b06-919a-7e2f047c2d37/0a454c70-1711-11ed-82db-9f73654e4206/file-1l6kp6abc.png?format=png\" data-orsrc=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/image/1l6kp6abb/cd2e5b45-a0bb-4b06-919a-7e2f047c2d37/0a454c70-1711-11ed-82db-9f73654e4206/file-1l6kp6abc.png\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"max-width:100%;height:auto;display:block;margin:0px auto;max-height:40vh\" alt=\"JEE Main 2022 (Online) 26th July Evening Shift Physics - Current Electricity Question 158 English\"></p>",
