  {
    "id": "KJJ5NkSjd7OZHgEl7j2eU",
    "questionNumber": 9,
    "questionText": "In a Wheatstone bridge(see fig.), Resistances P and Q are approximately equal. When R = 400 $$\\Omega $$, the bridge\nis balanced. On interchanging P and Q, the value of R, for balance, is 405 $$\\Omega $$. The value of X is close to :\n<br><br><img src=\"https://imagex.cdn.examgoal.net/BllXclOZMakXCyiT7/Rk4uDzDDRUVFiFmMNOyGVAfliP8wk/8wFKuWr7OBobhbpGbxJ21K/image.png\" style=\"max-width: 100%;  height: auto;display: block;margin: 0 auto;\" loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"JEE Main 2019 (Online) 11th January Morning Slot Physics - Current Electricity Question 295 English\">",
    "options": [
      "402.5 ohm",
      "401.5 ohm",
      "403.5 ohm",
      "404.5 ohm"
    ],
    "correctOption": 0,
    "correctAnswer": null,
    "questionType": "MCQ",
    "marks": 4,
    "negativeMarks": -1,
    "subject": "Physics",
    "topic": "wheatstone-bridge",
    "difficulty": "easy",
    "solution": "For a balanced bridge,\n<br><br>$${P \\over Q} = {{400} \\over X}$$  ......(i)\n<br><br>After interchanging P and Q,\n<br><br>$${Q \\over P} = {{405} \\over X}$$  ......(ii)\n<br><br>Multiplying equation (i) and (ii), we get\n<br><br>X<sup>2</sup> = 400$$ \\times $$405\n<br><br>$$ \\Rightarrow $$ X = $$\\sqrt {400 \\times 405} $$ = 402.5 $$\\Omega $$",
    "section": "A",
    "type": "SCQ"
  },
  {
    "id": "1ky3ysovo",
    "questionNumber": 3,
    "questionText": "Two ideal batteries of emf V<sub>1</sub> and V<sub>2</sub> and three resistances R<sub>1</sub>, R<sub>2</sub> and R<sub>3</sub> are connected as shown in the figure. The current in resistance R<sub>2</sub> would be zero if<br><br> <img src=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/fly/@width/image/1ky4iki7j/7a879e3a-b2cf-404b-84ee-14b0e303156b/f05f4300-6fc8-11ec-b60f-27942bef1403/file-1ky4iki7k.png?format=png\" data-orsrc=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/image/1ky4iki7j/7a879e3a-b2cf-404b-84ee-14b0e303156b/f05f4300-6fc8-11ec-b60f-27942bef1403/file-1ky4iki7k.png\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"max-width:100%;height:auto;display:block;margin:0px auto;max-height:40vh\" alt=\"JEE Advanced 2014 Paper 1 Offline Physics - Current Electricity Question 24 English\">",
