    "questionText": "In a Wheatstone's bridge, three resistance $$P, Q$$ and $$R$$ connected in the three arms and the fourth arm is formed by two resistances $${S_1}$$ and $${S_2}$$ connected in parallel. The condition for the bridge to be balanced will be ",
